CREATE TABLE Feedback (
  feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  listener_name VARCHAR(255),
  comment TEXT,
  rating INT,
  feedback_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE music_production (
    production_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    production_name VARCHAR(255),
    producer_name VARCHAR(255),
    release_date DATE,
    production_quality INT
);

CREATE TABLE Song (song_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
artist VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
